# JoyScroll Environment Variables

# Text-to-Speech Configuration
# The app uses free browser voices by default (British male voices when available)
# Add these API keys ONLY if you want premium AI voices (optional)

# Option 1: OpenAI TTS (good quality, affordable)
# Get API key from: https://platform.openai.com/
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Option 2: ElevenLabs (highest quality, but premium)
# Get API key from: https://elevenlabs.io/
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your_elevenlabs_api_key_here

# Option 3: Azure Cognitive Services (good quality, competitive pricing)
# Get API key from: https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/cognitive-services/speech-services/
# AZURE_SPEECH_KEY=your_azure_speech_key_here
# AZURE_SPEECH_REGION=your_azure_region_here

# Image Services (existing)
UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY=your_unsplash_access_key
PEXELS_API_KEY=your_pexels_api_key

# Note: At least one TTS API key is recommended for the British male AI voice
# The app will try them in order: ElevenLabs -> Azure -> OpenAI -> Browser fallback
# If no AI TTS keys are provided, the app will fall back to browser voices